<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/css/all.min.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- include the header partial view for the Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="display-4">Projects</h1>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <p class="lead">
                <b>Roster Mobile Application</b><br />
                Employees in the terminal operations department need to shift shifts. At present, most teams use the Roster Mobile System to arrange their basic shifts. I am assigned to provide assist services to this project.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <img src="img/project/rma-1.png" alt="RMA" style="width: 250px;" />
              <img src="img/project/rma-2.png" alt="RMA" style="width: 250px;" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="my-4">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <img src="img/project/ffs-1.png" alt="FFS" style="width: 640px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <p class="lead">
                <b>Fine Food System</b><br />
                An ordering website re-written from classic ASP to ASP.NET, with MYSQL as backend storage. We are required to strengthen the security level when cake is ordered by a customer, and then redirect to the payment gateway to proceed the purchase. I solely in charged in this project and upgraded the website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="my-4">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <p class="lead">
                <b>Barge Berthing Planning System</b><br />
                A internal console system used by the terminal staff, to control the crane, shipyard and lifting logic flow. It is a Windows application written in Java and stored in Oracle database, with tons of sub-systems. I am assigned to assist some of the program enchancements.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <img src="img/project/bbps-1.png" alt="BBPS" style="width: 310px;" />
              <img src="img/project/bbps-2.png" alt="BBPS" style="width: 310px;" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- include the header partial view for the Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

    <!-- embed js files -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>